{"h59e71f00g6fc1g4011gbc94g7d91c0054be6": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "e6d5ce58-7775-9077-c734-294e2b0078bb"], "hf6403df0gd8a5g44edg838egd5c5ce94cf00": ["I'm... cured.", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "676d2c56-a813-8153-e2f6-58cfd378f711"], "h58243dd0g5f3dg4022g9aa6g88e5d2fcd1d2": ["Cured? Were you sick?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "37ce04c1-3b53-9400-36e5-4497eec99d3b"], "h588f1deag3798g4a46g9214g84bad28d2e41": ["I'd the Bite... Laduguer's Bite... sickness worse than... death.", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "c2899dc7-e00c-6564-fd30-8c4690068948"], "h3426ce99gdeddg4275g8081gded09e569540": ["Hag turned me... to stone. Stopped the... spread. ", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "b1d95cd7-6b13-ca80-8af9-63cae481b6b7"], "ha8fae574g60f8g4b14g9ba3g4192d539322d": ["What is your name?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "136f2ae0-fa80-5215-116f-546765d5f06f"], "h434277ceg4df9g4f3dgb930g0512014d0e45": ["Efrin... Hammerborn...", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "6f57c81a-3ce6-0c42-23ec-a5ae95e4e474"], "h4242700ag229fg47f0ga3c1ge2bcb4231cac": ["What happened to you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "c4177f34-ffcc-0123-fefb-5ca1d57b6d84"], "h39a32a7eg6a95g44a8g9643g98251f4250b3": ["Got sick... had to leave home... leave my children...", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "ab2e137f-ec6a-92b9-1d14-fa3467d9c70a"], "h7e8defc8g3135g40d6g952egdd648ec272d2": ["... wonder what... they look like now...", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "3f4745e2-1d9d-23cd-4675-0c6f9eada512"], "hb489dff1g5c0bg4ac0gb75ag3bfa5e1e6c72": ["What can you tell me about the hag?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "6bcd8651-4e6e-fcc6-073f-05e9a42d86de"], "h805473b1ga2ebg4cd7g81c6g86cfd4c86951": ["She'll give you more... than you bargained... for...", "48062828-eb14-43ab-ac97-3d7ed6cb2ecd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "cc0af567-97bc-1baf-ad35-a510af8c400f"], "hf74a6766g89aag4342g969agd2e8188e4b63": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "d104e0a1-b569-5dea-e0e9-3cfa21626fc0"], "hfa0c2f8ege585g4092g823egb321bd9438c5": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_001_Dead.html", "6b8e0d66-5d39-91f1-a6ea-61cfeeabe51e"]}